snippet.textDisplay: This song came out when I hit rock bottom. It’s gotta great message. And I relate to so much of this shit that it’s crazy. I’m not sober right now. I’ve been on Meth since 2016. I just hope that I can get past all this shit I’m going through and maybe come back to this comment someday to let you all know that I’m doing way better and I had finally figured it out .. but as of right now. I’m really struggling. 2020 has been so hard and I’m still fighting but sometimes I have to stop and wonder what it is that I’m even fighting for.. I’m just kinda lost in the sauce these days. I could really use any positive vibes I can get right now. I love y’all. ❤️...
